==Formulae==
By the end of this module you will be expected to have learnt the following formulae:
* <math> \cosh x \equiv \frac{1}{2}( e^x + e^{-x} ) </math>
* <math> \sinh x \equiv \frac{1}{2}( e^x - e^{-x} ) </math>
* <math> \tanh x \equiv \frac{\sinh x}{\cosh x} </math>

